=1 |\nauthor=Josh L. Dickey|title=Bailee Madison rides rodeo pic|work=variety.com|accessdate=April 11, 2011|date=April 11, 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[A Taste of Romance]]'' || Hannah Callahan || Television Movie\n|-\n| 2012 || ''Smart Cookies'' || Daisy || Television Movie\n|-\n| 2013 || ''The Magic Bracelet'' || Ashley || Short film\n|-\n| 2013 || ''Half'' || Riley Young || Television Movie\n|-\n| 2013 || ''Pete's Christmas'' || Katie || Television Movie\n|-\n| 2014 || ''[[Northpole (film)|Northpole]]'' || Clementine || Television Movie\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Northpole (film)|Northpole: Open for Christmas]]'' || Clementine || Television Movie\n|-\n| 2016 || ''Annabelle Hooper and the Ghosts of Nantucket'' || Annabelle Hooper || Also producer\n|-\n| 2016 || ''Holiday Joy'' || Joy Hockstatter || Television Movie\n|-\n| 2016 || ''The Night Before Halloween'' || Megan || Television Movie\n|-\n| 2016 || ''Date with Love'' || Heidi Watts || Television Movie\n|-\n| 2017 || ''[[A Cowgirl's Story]]'' || Dusty Rhodes || Also producer\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[The Strangers: Prey at Night]]'' || Kinsey ||\n|-\n| 2020 || ''A Week Away'' || TBA || Post-Production\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[CSI: NY]]'' || Rose Duncan || Episode: \"[[Boo (CSI: NY episode)|Boo]]\"\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[House (TV series)|House]]'' || Lucy || Episode: \"[[Act Your Age (House episode)|Act Your Age]]\"\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[Unfabulous]]'' || Young Addie Singer || 2 episodes; <br> Guest role (Season 3)\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[Cory in the House]]'' || Maya || 2 episodes; <br> Guest role (Season 1)\n|-\n| 2008 || ''[[Terminator: The Sarah Connor Chronicles]]'' || Little Girl || Episode: \"[[What He Beheld (Terminator: The Sarah Connor Chronicles)|What He Beheld]]\"\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Law & Order: Special Victims Unit]]'' || Mackenzie Burton || Episode: \"Locum\"\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Hubworld]]'' || Herself || 1 epi