inger || 2 episodes; <br> Guest role (Season 3)\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[Cory in the House]]'' || Maya || 2 episodes; <br> Guest role (Season 1)\n|-\n| 2008 || ''[[Terminator: The Sarah Connor Chronicles]]'' || Little Girl || Episode: \"[[What He Beheld (Terminator: The Sarah Connor Chronicles)|What He Beheld]]\"\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Law & Order: Special Victims Unit]]'' || Mackenzie Burton || Episode: \"Locum\"\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Hubworld]]'' || Herself || 1 episode<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/followbailee/status/18021973590286336 |title=Twitter / Bailee Madison: Katie and I will be on the |publisher=Twitter.com |date=December 23, 2010 |accessdate=January 28, 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2010-2012 || ''[[R.L. Stine's The Haunting Hour]]'' || Lilly Carbo / Jenny / Becky || 4 episodes; <br> Guest role (Seasons 1-3)\n|-\n|  2011 || ''[[Wizards of Waverly Place]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/Exclusive-Disney-Channel-1024328.aspx?rss=breakingnews6|\nauthor=Megan Walsh-Boyle|title=Exclusive: Disney Channel Announces Season 4 of Wizards of Waverly Place|work=tvguide.com|accessdate=April 17, 2011}}</ref> || [[Max Russo|Maxine Russo]] || 6 episodes; <br> Recurring role (Season 4)\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Chase (2010 TV series)|Chase]]'' || Zoe || Episode: \"Father Figure\"\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Powers (FX TV series)|Powers]]'' || Calista || Pilot<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/06/pilot-castings-usas-overunder-finds-female-lead-young-actress-joins-powers/| author=Nellie Andreeva |title=Pilot Castings: USA's 'Over/Under' Finds Female Lead, Young Actress Joins 'Powers'|work=deadline.com|accessdate=June 16, 2011| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110706145249/http://www.deadline.com/2011/06/pilot-castings-usas-overunder-finds-female-lead-young-actress-joins-powers/| archivedate= July 6, 2011 | url-status= live}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2012\u201313, 2016 || ''[[Once Upon a Time (TV series)|Once Upon a Time]]'' || Young [[Snow White]] || 4 episodes; <br> Guest